TopicTitle: Is here non-RSS realistic tech tree plugin?

Articles.Content:
I have a LOT of mods - almost 80. 30 mods are adding parts. Is here realistic tech tree, where you unlock basic parts first and moves forward?

Vanilla tree is kiiiinda useless for this 30 mods, that add parts.

Here is my modlist, that PartCatalog filtered - as in having parts.

Squad (DUH)

AreojetKerbodyne

B9 Areospace

BoJan (Quantum struts)

Deadly Reentry

Extraplanetary Launchpads

Firespitter

Hoogilan Labs (Adds floating parts, submarines and magic lander legs, that I didn't testd yet)

HullCameraVDS (Adds cameras)

KAS

Kethane

Klockheed_Martin (Asteroid Cities or something - makes asteroids useful)

KWRocketry

MagicSmokeIndustries (Infernal Robotics)

MechJeb2
